{"heading":"Children should honor their parents—Servants and masters are judged by the same law—Saints should put on the whole armor of God.","number":6,"verseCount":24,"verses":[[1,[["Children",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Children","tg/children"],"."]]],", ",["obey",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Counsel","tg/counsel"],"; ",["Family, Children, Duties of","tg/family-children-duties-of"],"; ",["Respect","tg/respect"],"."]]]," your parents in the Lord: for this is right."]],[2,[["Honour",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Honoring Father and Mother","tg/honoring-father-and-mother"],"."]]]," thy father and mother; (which is the first commandment with promise;)"]],[3,["That it may be well with thee, and thou mayest live long on the earth."]],[4,["And, ye ",["fathers",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Family, Love within","tg/family-love-within"],"; ",["Family, Patriarchal","tg/family-patriarchal"],"; ",["Marriage, Fatherhood","tg/marriage-fatherhood"],"."]]],", ",["provoke",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Provoking","tg/provoking"],"."]]]," not your ",["children",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward","tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"],"."]]]," to wrath: but bring them up in the nurture and admonition of the Lord."]],[5,[["Servants",["study-note-ref","a",[["Titus 2:9","nt/titus/2.9"],"."]]],", be obedient to them that are ",["your",["clarity-word"]]," ",["masters",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Pet. 2:18 (13–25)","nt/1-pet/2.18"],"."]]]," according to the flesh, with fear and trembling, in singleness of your heart, as unto Christ;"]],[6,["Not with eyeservice, as menpleasers; but as the ",["servants",["study-note-ref","a",[["1 Cor. 7:22 (21–24)","nt/1-cor/7.22"],"."]]]," of Christ, doing the ",["will",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Will of","tg/god-will-of"],"."]]]," of God from the heart;"]],[7,["With good will doing ",["service",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Service","tg/service"],"."]]],", as to the Lord, and not to men:"]],[8,["Knowing that whatsoever good thing any man doeth, the same shall he ",["receive",["study-note-ref","a",[["Col. 3:24","nt/col/3.24"],"."]]]," of the Lord, whether ",["he be",["clarity-word"]]," bond or free."]],[9,["And, ye ",["masters",["study-note-ref","a",[["Mal. 3:5","ot/mal/3.5"],"; ",["Col. 4:1","nt/col/4.1"],"."]]],", do the same things unto them, forbearing threatening: knowing that your ",["Master",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Leadership","tg/leadership"],"."]]]," also is in heaven; neither is there ",["respect",["study-note-ref","c",[["Moro. 8:12","bofm/moro/8.12"],"; ",["D&C 38:16","dc-testament/dc/38.16"],"."]]]," of persons with him."]],[10,["Finally, my brethren, be ",["strong",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Strength","tg/strength"],"."]]]," in the Lord, and in the power of his might."]],[11,["Put on the whole ",["armour",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 91:4","ot/ps/91.4"],"; ",["Rom. 13:12","nt/rom/13.12"],"; ",["2 Cor. 10:4 (3–6)","nt/2-cor/10.4"],"; ",["1 Thes. 5:8","nt/1-thes/5.8"],"; ",["D&C 27:15 (15–18)","dc-testament/dc/27.15"],". ",["TG Chastity","tg/chastity"],"; ",["Protection, Divine","tg/protection-divine"],"; ",["Watch","tg/watch"],"."]]]," of God, that ye may be able to stand against the wiles of the devil."]],[12,["For we ",["wrestle",["study-note-ref","a",[["JS—H 1:15 (15–17)","pgp/js-h/1.15"],"."]]]," not ",["against",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Opposition","tg/opposition"],"."]]]," ",["flesh and blood",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Flesh and Blood","tg/flesh-and-blood"],"."]]],", but against principalities, against powers, against the ",["rulers",["study-note-ref","d",[["2 Cor. 4:4","nt/2-cor/4.4"],"."]]]," of the ",["darkness",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Darkness, Spiritual","tg/darkness-spiritual"],"; ",["Secret Combinations","tg/secret-combinations"],"."]]]," of this world, against spiritual ",["wickedness",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG Governments","tg/governments"],"; ",["Wickedness","tg/wickedness"],"."]]]," in high ",["places.",["clarity-word"]]]],[13,["Wherefore take unto you the whole armour of God, that ye may be able to withstand in the evil day, and having done all, to stand."]],[14,["Stand therefore, having your loins ",["girt",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 11:5","ot/isa/11.5"],"."]]]," about with ",["truth",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Truth","tg/truth"],"."]]],", and having on the ",["breastplate",["study-note-ref","c",[["Isa. 59:17","ot/isa/59.17"],"; ",["61:10","ot/isa/61.10"],"."]]]," of ",["righteousness",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Righteousness","tg/righteousness"],"."]]],";"]],[15,["And your feet shod with the preparation of the gospel of ",["peace",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Peace of God","tg/peace-of-god"],"."]]],";"]],[16,["Above all, taking the shield of ",["faith",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Faith","tg/faith"],"."]]],", wherewith ye shall be able to quench all the fiery ",["darts",["study-note-ref","b",[["1 Ne. 15:24","bofm/1-ne/15.24"],"; ",["D&C 3:8","dc-testament/dc/3.8"],"."]]]," of the wicked."]],[17,["And take the helmet of ",["salvation",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Salvation","tg/salvation"],"."]]],", and the sword of the Spirit, which is the word of God:"]],[18,[["Praying",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Prayer","tg/prayer"],"."]]]," always with all prayer and supplication in the Spirit, and watching thereunto with all ",["perseverance",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Perseverance","tg/perseverance"],"."]]]," and supplication for all saints;"]],[19,["And for me, that utterance may be given unto me, that I may open my mouth boldly, to make known the ",["mystery",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Mysteries of Godliness","tg/mysteries-of-godliness"],"."]]]," of the gospel,"]],[20,["For which I am an ambassador in bonds: that therein I may speak ",["boldly",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 60:2 (2–3)","dc-testament/dc/60.2"],"."]]],", as I ought to speak."]],[21,["But that ye also may know my affairs, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," how I do, ",["Tychicus",["study-note-ref","a",[["Acts 20:4","nt/acts/20.4"],"."]]],", a beloved brother and faithful minister in the Lord, shall make known to you all things:"]],[22,["Whom I have sent unto you for the same purpose, that ye might know our affairs, and ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," he might comfort your hearts."]],[23,["Peace ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," to the brethren, and love with faith, from God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."]],[24,["Grace ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," with all them that love our Lord Jesus Christ in ",["sincerity",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Sincere","tg/sincere"],"."]]],". Amen."]]],"volume":"nt"}